Tips on how to ship your item
Find the lightest packaging material as possible to minimize shipping cost, i.e. poly mailers or padded envelopes. Boxes are best for larger, more delicate items.
Wrap delicate items in tissue paper or bubble wrap and place it in the envelope or box. You can add packaging peanuts to the box if you have room left over.
Use any printer to print a discounted shipping label directly from eBay and tape it to the package.
